02:47:05.316 --> 02:47:06.969
I just would like to have a fresh start.

02:47:06.969 --> 02:47:10.376
Would you pray for me?

02:47:10.376 --> 02:47:13.013
' I believe you're not here by coincidence.

02:47:13.013 --> 02:47:17.264
You're here because the Lord called you here tonight.

02:47:17.264 --> 02:47:24.140
You know you were at your relatives over Thanksgiving yesterday and you're just like, 'Man, they're all miserable.

02:47:35.657 --> 02:47:36.080
I don't want to be a part of that.

02:47:36.080 --> 02:47:37.550
I'm just searching for authenticity.

02:47:37.550 --> 02:47:39.920
' There's so much fakeness in churches nowadays.

02:47:39.920 --> 02:47:46.288
'I just want authentic Jesus, authentic relationship.

02:47:46.288 --> 02:47:49.288
Could you please pray for me?

02:47:49.288 --> 02:47:58.800
' Diana and I would love to pray for you, but I want you to be bold about your decision tonight and coming back to the Lord.

02:47:59.424 --> 02:48:07.291
I want you to put in the comment section right now, 'I want to be saved' or 'I'm coming back to Jesus.

02:48:07.291 --> 02:48:11.680
' Jesus died for you publicly.

02:48:11.680 --> 02:48:14.773
Now I want you to do it publicly.

02:48:14.773 --> 02:48:15.787
It's easy.

02:48:15.787 --> 02:48:21.862
All you have to do is type in there right now, 'I want to be saved.

02:48:29.260 --> 02:48:29.520
I need Jesus Christ.

02:48:29.520 --> 02:48:31.935
I'm coming back to the Lord.

02:48:31.935 --> 02:48:36.093
' Tonight, I'm coming back to Jesus.

02:48:37.520 --> 02:48:44.830
And if that's you and we're speaking to you, you feel that tugging at your heart, that's Jesus knocking on your door.

02:48:44.830 --> 02:48:49.724
He's knocking on the door of your heart right now and he's saying, 'Will you just let me in?

02:48:49.724 --> 02:48:52.000
Will you give me a chance?

02:48:52.000 --> 02:48:57.454
' He's never left you and he's never forsaken you.

02:48:57.454 --> 02:49:02.240
He said he'll be with you always, but you can walk away from him.

02:49:02.240 --> 02:49:03.759
He'll never walk away from you.

02:49:03.759 --> 02:49:09.970
The Bible says that he would rather you be hot or cold, but if we're lukewarm, he said he'd spew us out of his mouth.

02:49:09.970 --> 02:49:12.729
So tonight, it's time for you to come back to the Father.

02:49:12.729 --> 02:49:19.752
It's time for you to be all in, to sell out to Jesus once again and say, 'God, I want to make a new start.

02:49:19.752 --> 02:49:22.340
' I'm going to say a simple prayer with you.

02:49:22.340 --> 02:49:32.422
And if you're here and that speaks to you and this altar call is for you and you say, 'Brandon, pray for me,' I want to pray for you.

02:49:32.422 --> 02:49:39.066
Let's just say this prayer, and after that, we're going to tell you what to do next.

02:49:52.653 --> 02:49:53.067
Say, 'Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

02:49:53.067 --> 02:49:59.520
' I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

02:50:00.183 --> 02:50:05.320
I believe you're making intercession for me at the right hand of the Father even right now.

02:50:05.320 --> 02:50:08.640
Jesus, I turn my back on the world.

02:50:19.000 --> 02:50:19.250
I turn my back on the devil.

02:50:45.920 --> 02:50:46.260
I turn my back on my sin.

02:50:46.260 --> 02:50:50.008
Jesus, I ask you to forgive me and wash me clean.

02:50:50.008 --> 02:50:54.432
Father, I thank you, Lord, that tonight I have a fresh, clean start.

02:50:54.432 --> 02:50:56.980
Jesus, I make you my Lord and my personal Savior.

02:50:56.980 --> 02:50:59.530
From this day forward, Lord, I'll serve you.

02:50:59.530 --> 02:51:05.691
From this day forward, Lord, I make you the Lord of my life.

02:51:05.691 --> 02:51:14.340
Jesus, I ask you to write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

02:51:14.340 --> 02:51:21.336
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're doing that right now for me.

02:51:21.336 --> 02:51:27.460
Lord, I serve you from this day forward.

02:51:27.460 --> 02:51:36.051
Lord, I thank you that you've forgiven me and you cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

02:51:36.051 --> 02:51:39.520
God, I love you and I'm excited to come home.

02:51:39.520 --> 02:51:43.760
I'm excited to be a part of the family in the mighty name of Jesus.

02:51:43.760 --> 02:51:44.471
Amen and amen.

02:51:46.594 --> 02:51:52.293
I believe if you just said that prayer, it's a simple little prayer.

02:51:58.640 --> 02:51:59.540
It doesn't have to be all religious; it's just from the heart.

02:52:08.450 --> 02:52:09.430
The Bible says with the heart, confession is made unto salvation.

02:52:09.430 --> 02:52:13.712
I believe right now that you accepted Jesus Christ.

02:52:13.712 --> 02:52:17.760
Now, what do you do after that?

02:52:17.760 --> 02:52:19.680
Well, you find a Bible-believing church.

02:52:19.680 --> 02:52:23.188
I'd go to a non-denominational church.

02:52:23.188 --> 02:52:27.879
I would get plugged in there.

02:52:34.000 --> 02:52:34.320
I would tell the pastor there, 'I need to be water-baptized.

02:52:43.040 --> 02:52:43.291
Please, water-baptized me.

02:52:43.291 --> 02:52:44.046
' Volunteer.

02:52:44.046 --> 02:52:52.070
Whatever you can do to get plugged into that church.

02:52:52.080 --> 02:52:58.800
Read your Bible every day and pray, and come over here and pray with us.

02:53:03.467 --> 02:53:03.893
If you don't have a Bible, we want to give you your first Bible as a Christian.

02:53:03.893 --> 02:53:06.937
Our ministry will love you.

02:53:06.937 --> 02:53:20.000
We want to celebrate your decision tonight of coming to Jesus, and we're excited you're a part of the family.

02:53:20.000 --> 02:53:21.893
Welcome to the family.

02:53:21.893 --> 02:53:28.186
Diana will tell you how to get your Bible.

02:53:28.186 --> 02:53:40.217
Yes, if you would just go down to the description of this video, you will find our email address.

02:53:40.217 --> 02:53:53.733
In the subject line of the email, just put 'I need a Bible' and then put your name and address in the body of the email and we will get one to you.

02:53:58.720 --> 02:53:58.960
And we just want to say congratulations.

02:53:58.960 --> 02:54:01.600
It's the best decision you've ever made in your life.

02:54:01.600 --> 02:54:02.800
Welcome to the family.

02:54:02.800 --> 02:54:05.978
Jesus is rejoicing and Satan's going, 'Man, we just lost a great sinner.

02:54:05.978 --> 02:54:06.742
' The devil's upset.

02:54:06.742 --> 02:54:09.840
He said, 'We just lost a good sinner, boys.

02:54:09.840 --> 02:54:11.440
' Welcome home.

02:54:11.440 --> 02:54:13.269
Welcome to the family.

02:54:13.269 --> 02:54:20.064
48 people gave their heart to Jesus Christ tonight.

02:54:20.064 --> 02:54:25.298
There's so many people that you can't trust, but you can trust Him.

02:54:25.298 --> 02:54:25.700
Jesus.

02:54:25.700 --> 02:54:28.010
He'll never leave you and He'll never forsake you.

02:54:28.010 --> 02:54:33.213
Out of anybody in this whole world you could ever trust, it'd be Him.

02:54:33.213 --> 02:54:35.240
He'll never leave you.

02:54:35.240 --> 02:54:35.840
Never.

02:54:35.840 --> 02:54:37.760
You're safe with Him.

02:54:37.760 --> 02:54:39.706
Behold, He makes all things new.

02:54:39.706 --> 02:54:42.260
All 48 of you, welcome to the family.

02:54:42.260 --> 02:54:43.310
Yesterday we had 38.

02:54:43.310 --> 02:54:44.480
Day before yesterday, 38.

02:54:44.480 --> 02:54:45.780
Now I have 48.

02:54:53.408 --> 02:54:53.632
So all glory to Jesus.

02:54:53.632 --> 02:54:55.246
We're excited you're here.

02:54:55.246 --> 02:54:56.800
Praise the Lord.

02:54:56.800 --> 02:55:07.990
Thank you for joining us.

02:55:08.000 --> 02:55:09.830
How did we meet?

02:55:09.830 --> 02:55:11.520
We met at a Bible study.

02:55:11.520 --> 02:55:14.693
She didn't want to go to it.

02:55:14.693 --> 02:55:17.888
It was a friend of ours.

02:55:17.888 --> 02:55:28.584
Well, her mom—I didn't want to go either, but my sister was going to the Bible study because her friend's name was Jennifer.

02:55:28.584 --> 02:55:35.540
Diana—my friend wasn't coming, so she wasn't going, so I wasn't going to go.

02:55:35.540 --> 02:55:40.720
It was a Christmas party, but my mom made me.

02:55:40.720 --> 02:55:45.480
She said she wouldn't go and I wasn't going to go.

02:55:45.480 --> 02:55:57.333
My sister went and she didn't want to drive by herself across town, and I told my sister, 'Let's go, I'll go with you.

02:55:57.333 --> 02:56:04.052
' So I went because they were having food and I was like, 'Let's go and eat.

02:56:04.052 --> 02:56:15.396
' They had pizza and stuff and they were having a Christmas party and she came to the party and we were doing a Bible study.

02:56:27.520 --> 02:56:27.872
It was Jeremy Pearsons' Bible study.

02:56:27.872 --> 02:56:31.310
He has a church in Colorado Springs now.

02:56:31.310 --> 02:56:38.999
Jeremy Pearsons had a Bible study there and he invited me to come and I said, 'Well, we'll go.

02:56:38.999 --> 02:56:44.098
' So I went with my sister after he invited us and she was there.

02:56:44.098 --> 02:56:47.369
It was at a girl named Jennifer's house.

02:56:47.369 --> 02:56:55.039
Her mom was the head prayer lady at the church; her name was Jennifer Jennings.

02:57:11.680 --> 02:57:11.960
I met her there and we've talked ever since.

02:57:11.960 --> 02:57:12.800
Long time.

02:57:12.800 --> 02:57:14.142
God is so good.

02:57:14.142 --> 02:57:15.920
Met her at a Bible study.

02:57:15.920 --> 02:57:16.580
Jeremy Pearsons.

02:57:16.580 --> 02:57:17.680
Now, Pastor Jeremy Pearsons.

02:57:17.680 --> 02:57:19.680
And he is amazing.

02:57:19.680 --> 02:57:22.990
Like the Lord sent him just for me.

02:57:22.990 --> 02:57:24.880
He truly is a soulmate.

02:57:24.880 --> 02:57:26.784
He really is my soulmate.

02:57:26.784 --> 02:57:28.720
There's no other person I know.

02:57:28.720 --> 02:57:34.400
Right from the get-go, even when we were dating, he was always listening to Brother Hagin.

02:57:34.400 --> 02:57:38.733
I've listened to Kenneth Hagin since I was like 12 years old.

02:57:38.733 --> 02:57:40.222
Truly on fire for the Lord.

02:57:45.560 --> 02:57:45.920
And that is such a rarity even these days.

02:57:45.920 --> 02:57:50.990
Even when we were younger, you couldn't find anybody like that at that age.

02:57:52.920 --> 02:57:55.880
I always had a problem because I couldn't read and do everything in school.

02:58:01.250 --> 02:58:02.989
Because I was bullied so much, when the teacher asked me, 'What do you want to do when you grow up?

02:58:02.989 --> 02:58:06.480
' I said, 'I want to be a preacher.

02:58:06.480 --> 02:58:11.348
' Even when I was in middle school, truly, that's all I've ever known.

02:58:21.200 --> 02:58:21.440
So that's all we talked about.

02:58:21.440 --> 02:58:48.350
He would say, 'This is what tape I've listened to today,' and he would give it to me and I would listen to it.

02:58:48.350 --> 02:58:53.240
Every single time I got paid, they had a bookstore called WordWorks.

02:58:53.240 --> 02:59:25.964
I'd go into the WordWorks bookstore and they would have Brother Hagin CDs and tapes, and I would buy those tapes every single time I got paid and I would listen to them for the whole two weeks until I got paid again.

02:59:26.266 --> 02:59:32.925
I would be so excited to get one tape series and I'd listen to that over and over again.

02:59:41.969 --> 02:59:48.160
Then I would say, 'When are you going to be done with that so I can listen to it?

02:59:48.160 --> 02:59:54.000
' He was like, 'I'm going to listen to it one more time, then you can have it.

02:59:54.000 --> 03:00:01.644
' I had so many tapes and all this stuff, but when they stopped dealing with tapes, I didn't have them anymore.

03:00:01.644 --> 03:00:04.528
Now I find all that stuff on YouTube.

03:00:04.528 --> 03:00:07.824
Brother Hagin, his ministry put it all on YouTube.

03:00:26.071 --> 03:00:26.302
So you don't have to have a tape player where you have to flip it over to hear the conclusion.

03:00:26.302 --> 03:00:29.976
Now it's all on YouTube; it's easy and it's free.

03:00:29.976 --> 03:00:33.400
You just push the button and it's right there.

03:00:33.400 --> 03:00:36.759
Thank God all those treasures are on YouTube.

03:00:45.543 --> 03:00:45.840
The younger generation doesn't even know what cassette tapes are.

03:00:46.009 --> 03:00:49.220
I had cassette tapes everywhere and I listened to the Word continually.

03:00:49.220 --> 03:00:56.080
When I was cleaning, doing bathrooms, or mowing outside, I just had my Walkman in my coat with the headphones in my ears.

03:00:58.853 --> 03:01:00.596
The Lord spoke to me about those wireless headphones that Braden had on all the time.

03:01:00.818 --> 03:01:09.829
I won't say a brand, but he had them on and the Lord said, 'Tell him to get those off his head.

03:01:09.829 --> 03:01:12.080
' There's danger in those.

03:01:12.080 --> 03:01:19.840
So, we don't use those wireless headphones anymore that send a signal.

03:01:19.840 --> 03:01:23.138
The Lord said, "There's danger.

03:01:23.138 --> 03:01:24.471
Take that off.

03:01:26.260 --> 03:01:29.200
" And I was just praying in the spirit and I heard him.

03:01:29.200 --> 03:01:31.760
So, we got rid of those wireless things that have the signal.

03:01:32.720 --> 03:01:34.160
I don't know why, but it's like me.

03:01:36.969 --> 03:01:38.462
I don't put a cell phone up to my head.

03:01:54.260 --> 03:01:54.510
I talk like this.

03:01:55.510 --> 03:02:07.828
I put on speakerphone when I talk because the Lord said, when I was in there, "Don't put that phone up to your head anymore.

03:02:17.813 --> 03:02:18.186
" And he said, "You know, don't carry it around in your pocket that much.

03:02:29.820 --> 03:02:30.190
Don't keep that thing on your body all the time.

03:02:44.770 --> 03:02:44.960
" And I didn't know.

03:02:51.600 --> 03:03:08.297
And even whenever I sleep at night, I keep that further over here and don't let that be next to you.

03:03:08.297 --> 03:03:10.080
There's danger there.

03:03:15.659 --> 03:03:16.039
I don't understand, but I just listen to him.

03:03:16.419 --> 03:03:18.652
I pray and I obey.

03:03:34.320 --> 03:03:34.560
When he says to do something, I just do it.

03:03:41.839 --> 03:03:42.026
Don't do that.

03:03:42.026 --> 03:03:45.136
Don't put those things in your ears all the time.

03:03:45.136 --> 03:03:46.845
You know, they're wireless.

03:03:46.845 --> 03:03:48.399
Don't do that.

03:03:48.399 --> 03:03:50.350
And I said, "What?

03:03:50.350 --> 03:03:51.780
" There's signals there.

03:03:51.780 --> 03:03:52.820
There's something wrong.

03:03:52.820 --> 03:03:54.347
Don't do it.

03:03:54.347 --> 03:03:58.080
Just don't do it.

03:04:18.640 --> 03:04:18.1000
So, Braden gives things wires now.

03:04:18.1000 --> 03:04:20.920
But just things like that.

03:04:20.920 --> 03:04:24.640
I don't know why I got off on that, but that was important.

03:04:24.640 --> 03:04:27.080
The Lord says, "Say that.

03:04:27.080 --> 03:04:28.199
" I said it.

03:04:28.199 --> 03:04:35.799
I don't know who that was for, but just pray about that.

03:04:35.799 --> 03:04:39.259
Having wireless things in your head all the time.

03:04:39.259 --> 03:04:40.240
Be careful; have wisdom.

03:04:40.240 --> 03:04:44.239
This new generation has their headphones on all the time.

03:05:00.869 --> 03:05:01.211
I had Walkmans on.

03:05:15.952 --> 03:05:16.240
That's where I was going with it.

03:05:17.840 --> 03:05:18.480
But I had a Walkman.

03:05:18.480 --> 03:05:20.720
We used to use the Walkman.

03:05:30.018 --> 03:05:32.229
I had a Walkman and I would always break that cord and I'd get my hand caught up in it and rip it out and I'd be like, "Oh.

03:05:33.120 --> 03:05:35.780
" And my mom would say, "Brandon, do you have to have another set?

03:05:35.780 --> 03:05:37.728
" I'd say, "Yeah, I ruined them again.

03:05:37.728 --> 03:05:39.989
" But we met at church.

03:05:39.989 --> 03:05:41.493
All glory to Jesus.

03:05:41.493 --> 03:05:42.782
Should I say more?

03:05:42.782 --> 03:05:44.280
So, is wired okay?

03:05:45.210 --> 03:05:45.520
I don't know.

03:05:45.520 --> 03:05:47.347
He didn't say wired were bad.

03:05:47.347 --> 03:05:50.080
He just said the unwired ones.

03:05:50.080 --> 03:05:55.840
He told me I use wired ones, but they don't send a Wi-Fi signal.

03:05:55.840 --> 03:05:58.240
Bluetooth.

03:06:09.520 --> 03:06:09.698
It was the Bluetooth signal that he was upset about when I was praying.

03:06:09.698 --> 03:06:13.700
He said, "Don't keep that on your head all the time.

03:06:13.700 --> 03:06:17.960
" Now, you do what you want to do.

03:06:28.720 --> 03:06:32.000
That's just what he told me.

03:06:32.000 --> 03:06:36.400
And he told my son because he said, "No more.

03:06:49.840 --> 03:06:50.100
Do not do that no more.

03:06:50.100 --> 03:06:51.400
" And I said, "Okay.

03:06:51.400 --> 03:06:56.000
" So, I obeyed and we got the ones with the wire.

03:07:15.560 --> 03:07:15.810
They have good ones with wires and he just hooks it up to his laptop and stuff.

03:07:16.857 --> 03:07:21.519
And yeah, you can get some pretty good ones still with wires, but they're not noise-canceling.

03:07:24.160 --> 03:07:29.556
I think that's what everybody wants is noise-canceling, but that's not really good for you.

03:07:32.479 --> 03:07:32.772
I see.

03:07:32.772 --> 03:07:33.653
What else?

03:07:33.946 --> 03:07:35.870
I was looking at your comments.

03:07:35.870 --> 03:07:36.620
"Hello, Britney.

03:07:36.620 --> 03:07:42.000
Could you listen to some stuff you learned?

03:07:42.000 --> 03:07:43.850
" What does that mean?

03:08:14.319 --> 03:08:14.559
I don't understand.

03:08:15.520 --> 03:08:21.109
I think they're asking whenever you learned how to pray.

03:08:21.109 --> 03:08:26.570
Whenever you said this word to them when you learned how to pray.

03:08:26.570 --> 03:08:28.027
Pastor Terry didn't put that stuff public.

03:08:28.027 --> 03:08:38.251
She did prayer school on Thursdays and Pastor Terry was in there and Gina and Annie Bin-Hof was the lady's name at the time.

03:08:42.000 --> 03:08:42.213
I remember they would pray on Thursdays.

03:08:42.213 --> 03:08:50.029
Then I would sit in there and listen to them and then Jennifer when they would all have prayer.

03:09:00.206 --> 03:09:01.160
I just listened to prayer and I got stirred up by it as a kid; the impartation was there.

03:09:01.160 --> 03:09:03.940
I've always been drawn to it.

03:09:03.940 --> 03:09:09.1000
My first vision was when I was 14 years old.

03:09:09.1000 --> 03:09:17.919
My mom had a friend that was going through a hard time and I was praying.

03:09:17.919 --> 03:09:28.079
My brother and I shared bunk beds and I was praying on the bottom bunk.

03:09:35.700 --> 03:09:35.920
I was on the bed and I was praying.

03:09:38.384 --> 03:09:43.347
I was laying like this and all of a sudden heat like fire hit my head and it was my first vision I ever had.

03:09:57.024 --> 03:09:57.248
And it went over me and my ear started burning like fire, like a match tip.

03:09:57.248 --> 03:09:58.816
And I started seeing that.

03:09:58.816 --> 03:10:00.720
That was the first vision I ever had.

03:10:00.720 --> 03:10:02.640
I'll never forget my first vision.

03:10:02.640 --> 03:10:08.800
And from that point on, it's grown more and more when I pray.

03:10:26.960 --> 03:10:27.310
And so I've just been walking in this.

03:10:30.180 --> 03:10:30.809
And I learned then because I always loved prayer.

03:10:31.019 --> 03:10:45.289
I listened to Sister Wilkerson, Jeannie Wilkerson, and I'd listen to old tapes from her because Pastor Terry had archives in the Word Works, and we would take those archives and I would listen to them on a Walkman.

03:10:45.289 --> 03:10:47.897
There were tapes from Jeannie Wilkerson.

03:10:47.897 --> 03:11:01.560
I listened to those because there was no YouTube back then.

03:11:01.560 --> 03:11:04.830
Yes, he did have hair.

03:11:04.830 --> 03:11:05.640
People were...

03:11:05.640 --> 03:11:08.160
I had a lot of hair.

03:11:08.160 --> 03:11:10.773
In fact, I used to flip my bangs.

03:11:10.773 --> 03:11:14.800
I had a lot of hair.

03:11:38.719 --> 03:11:39.039
I don't know what happened.

03:11:39.039 --> 03:11:45.520
In fact, I'd put gel in and spike it up.

03:11:45.822 --> 03:11:46.729
I looked good.

03:11:46.729 --> 03:11:51.531
When I get to heaven, I'm going to have hair again.

03:11:51.531 --> 03:11:51.702
I've seen it.

03:11:57.645 --> 03:11:58.022
And the Lord showed me what I look like.

03:12:09.053 --> 03:12:09.439
You saw it yourself?

